#

Grilled Chicken Pesto Burger

$12.5
550 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

DairyNuts

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

GrilledBurgerChickenGourmet

Description

A juicy grilled chicken burger topped with vibrant pesto, creamy mozzarella, and fresh basil for a burst of flavor.

Ingredients

  • Ground chicken: 1 lb
  • Pesto sauce: 1/4 cup
  • Fresh mozzarella cheese: 4 slices
  • Fresh basil leaves: 1/2 cup
  • Garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Burger buns: 4
